{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_glady_set_1", "eventName": "失水症", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "失水症", "storyInfo": "歌蕾蒂婭追蹤著阿戈爾技術，摧毀了一處深海教會的試驗場，並獲知還有其他獵人倖存。此時，有人出現並提議合作。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "5:18 P.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊比利亞普利瑪維拉城 某教堂內"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibchurch", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 50.0, "duration": 1.5, "ease": "OutQuad", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  咦，長椅上什麼時候多了個人？", "name": "虔誠的青年"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  女士，您一直坐在這裡嗎？", "name": "虔誠的青年"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我剛剛走過的時候，並沒有注意到您......", "name": "虔誠的青年"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我看到您正在投入地使用這把......由某種植物器官製成的工具打磨地面。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呃，您是想說掃帚？是的，我是在掃地。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  請您諒解，我無意打擾您的工作，畢竟看起來您還需要忙很久。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不，沒關係哈哈，這算不上工作，我只是個普通的信徒，偶爾過來幫忙打掃教堂而已。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  之前我並沒有見過您。您也是阿戈爾人嗎？", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......阿戈爾？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這個“也”字或許沒那麼準確。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  抱、抱歉！那一定是我誤解了，我不是故意把您當作我們中的一員......", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在生理層面，您並沒有看錯。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哦......那您是來自別的城市嗎？", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可以這麼說。我剛來幾個月。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這趟旅途，對我們阿戈爾人來說一定不太容易。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  的確令人疲憊。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  有什麼問題的話，您隨便開口......", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好。既然您仍願意以阿戈爾自稱，我不禁產生了一絲疑問——", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們曾經所屬的國度，清潔機器全天無休，不會容許街道上沾有一點灰塵。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  請問你們是如何忍受眼前這種骯髒低效的生活的？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，大家也都不想的。五十多年前的那場災難改變了伊比利亞。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  伊比利亞？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不，我指的並非這個陸上國家。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那您說的......是曾經那些阿戈爾聚落？", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我只聽爺爺說過，咳，女士，現在那些水下城市都廢棄了。他們說這很危險，無論對我們島民，還是對伊比利亞來說都是。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們聽從了那群鳥兒的話。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  儘管只是皮毛，你們還是攜帶著一部分阿戈爾的知識與技術。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們為何會自認為比陸地上的野蠻人還要低等？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  也......不是說低等，但......女士，這些話還是別讓懲戒軍聽到了。我們還能留在這座封鎖線附近的城市並不容易......", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  怯懦，並且猶疑。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在阿戈爾，但凡有孩子出現這樣的問題，他們的父母都會被法律剝奪教養後代的機會。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊......這聽起來有點恐怖。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  恐怖嗎？看來你們完全忘記了自己本來是如何生活的。陸地上的人已經完全將你們同化。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在伊比利亞這個地方生活，表現得和大家太不一樣，是一件很危險的事。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我理解你們的選擇。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......女士，您看起來有些失望。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  失望的前提是有過希望。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  或許你們帶上岸的不止於此，但顯然，要找起來還需要花一些時間。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  女士，您說的這些話，我起碼有一半沒聽懂。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我對這種交流方式還不太熟悉。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您的措辭也......很古怪，有點像幾十年前流行過的諷刺歌舞劇......", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那些藝術作品已經不再流行？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  很遺憾。我還挺欣賞它們的。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  原來您是因為喜歡才學了這種語調......", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所以，你們並不會通過影音存儲碟片快速掌握一門陌生語言？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......還真不會。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可以理解。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  大概也不是因為我們太笨......", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當然能有別的說法。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呼......女士，要是我又冒犯到您的話，我先道個歉......您看起來心情不太好，您是不是生病了？", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  陸地上的病原體還不至於能對我的身體機能造成損傷。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  至於情緒不佳，也許是的，畢竟這裡太乾燥了。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......我只聽過大家抱怨這個季節的伊比利亞太潮濕。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  無論如何，您沒生病就好。當然，您要是哪裡不舒服，您也可以向教士求助。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  信仰。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們並不信仰科學和技術，也不信仰國家實體，卻把理想寄託在一個......缺乏可靠性的雜質上。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當然，我最近意識到，這也是你們借著資訊不對稱而實施互相欺騙的一種有效途徑。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您可能誤會了，我並不覺得翻閱經書或者聽一下佈道就能治病......", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  超出預期。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哈......哈哈......女士，您真的有種特別的幽默感。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我是想說，教會的人很慷慨，他們最近還幫忙收留了一些礦......呃，病人。他們和病人們也都是阿戈爾人。", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  除了與您這樣的“阿戈爾人”聊聊之外，您口中教會的行為也同時構成了我來到這裡的原因。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊？您是想來探望什麼病人嗎？", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  假如這裡確實有我想探望的人，那麼......", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  安東尼奧，西邊的窗戶怎麼破了一個大洞？", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  破洞？十分鐘前那砰的一下，太快了，我還以為是懲戒軍在抓人......", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我能否給您一個建議？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  女士，您想說什麼？", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  儘快離開。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  袖、袖標？懲戒軍袖標？您——您是懲戒軍的人？難怪您這麼奇特......我竟然沒意識到！", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  長官，謝、謝謝您放過我！我馬上就走！", "name": "虔誠的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  記得關上門。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibchurch", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "教會工作人員"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不錯。陸地上的軍隊組織雖然形式極其低效，士兵的技術也弱小得可憐，但對更弱小的人來說，威懾力依然能發揮作用。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  此外，我很高興看到你們都沒走。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這會為我省下一點時間。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  味道......", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  請再走近一些。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呵......呵呵......你不是懲戒軍......你想要什麼？", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我本以為你們會更能言善語一點。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  畢竟，當我觀察到你們正在使用的技術竟然要比那些脫逃者的更完整時，我曾對你們抱有過一絲期待。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......技術？我們不明白你在說什麼。", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  源石。這種危險與潛力並存的特殊能源在海底並不存在。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  對能源的好奇並不稀奇。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒人能把阿戈爾原樣地複製到陸地上，出於這個原因，我在這個名為伊比利亞的國家裡見到了大量與美觀毫不相關的技術雜合體。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  然而，你們和那些強迫自己融入到這個陸上國家的脫逃者不一樣，你們使用阿戈爾的技術提純源石，無疑有著另外的打算。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我們......幫忙......", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  慷慨地幫忙？只有稚嫩的人才會信。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  他們並沒有意識到那些病人最後都消失在了哪裡，而我在那些倒楣的實驗體身上找到了阿戈爾技術的痕跡。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你......發現了？", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  毫無難度。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  想要把一個個體轉化成另外的形式，這樣的技術需要經過幾十道程序。你們所做的到了哪一步？第一道程序，還是第二道？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那次接觸之前就上岸了的脫逃者，他們不可能掌握這些程序。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  海洋與大陸之間的通道已被它們所占，如果連我都無法回去，你們就也不可能通過正常手段出來。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  早已習慣在陸地上行走的你們，是如何做到還與海洋保持著聯繫？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  還是說......有人把海裡最骯髒的垃圾也帶上了岸？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你是誰？", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我厭倦了這種互相指認的把戲，這俗套到不應出現在陸地上的劇作裡。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭輕輕揮了下她的槊。陸地上並不存在的合金以肉眼無法看清的速度觸到了石磚，以她為圓心，整個教堂的地面轟然塌陷。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_undergroud_u_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如我所料。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們特地把這種低劣的試驗場所建在假模假式的建築之下，就為了騙過陸地人的眼睛？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而且，這些卑小的伎倆竟然真能獲得顯著的成效。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我又該重新評估這些陸地國家的組織水準了。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  咳......咳咳！你這把武器！還有你的力量......這是源石技藝？", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呵，源石技藝。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不，不可能......你......你是......", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果......你是主教他們提到過的......那你在幾個月前早就受了重傷！", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們知道三個月前在海底發生的事？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們在岸上見過其他人。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們見到的，是誰？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這速度......呵......呵......你剛才為什麼不動？", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在陸地上移動太累了。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果站著不動就能把你們這些不像話的垃圾清除，我為什麼要花費這個力氣？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我......我不知道......我們只是守著......你不能破壞這裡......", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  確實。你們太低級了，掌握的資訊有限。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那我只能換一些問題。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們在陸地上還有多少個體？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們對阿戈爾還有多少圖謀？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  還有，為什麼，你們在研究源石與阿戈爾人身體的人為結合？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呵......呵......呵......味道......", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  別白費勁了。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  變成恐魚，只會讓你死得更快。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不......不會......啊啊啊啊——！", "name": "教會工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  正好。（阿戈爾語）我也想求你們死得快一點。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  脆弱到輕輕一劃拉，就全碎了。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呃——", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這種......胃裡的絞痛......又來了。自從上岸，就沒停過。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這些連恐魚都變不完全的蠢貨......我竟然只配在這裡殺死這樣的獵物！", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  還有那些......上了岸的阿戈爾人，他們都變得和陸地人沒有區別。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  從離開海水，到身體裡最後一絲水分蒸發，需要多少時間？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這種結局，和另一種，無論哪種都......", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不......我不能......！", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （嘔吐）", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但是......", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......是不是真的還有人活著？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果還有人活著，我要花多少時間才能救回他們？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "歌蕾蒂婭感到自己體內的溫度和體表一樣仍在急遽地上升。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  別停下來，廢物。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  即便無法回到阿戈爾......不，正是因為暫時回不去，我才必須這麼做。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "找回我的獵人，繼續履行我的職責。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "一刻不停地戰鬥下去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "——為了阿戈爾。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 3